><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffcf4346e22ec1d9b0a2375ad01b63ee59fd311a","tid":2461431,"uid":28449,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"quote":{"pid":"ba28003c06021e0313af614cf2d1d1370d007570","tid":2461431,"uid":353267,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"識人做咗成年 一張單都冇<br />\n係好多人都係咁 定佢特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"我自己都做過幾間行，中美利港21，以前一入行吾讓做，跟錯人，翻工漫無目的，吾識搵客，由得我自己企係示範單位撈客，但後來跟咗朋友做，搵啱方法，努力付出先有今日少少回報。<br />\n<br />\n呢行門檻太低，咩人都可以入行，但我自己認為，跟啱人最重要，你嘅能力值取決於身邊五個人平均值，好多人入行之後，吾識做，冇方向，個經理又唔理，吾翻工，所以好多人一年食白果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d0f82658a64b164f95453cebe77807e4ffdfda","tid":2461431,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:03:15.000Z","msg":"冇可能，少吹水"},{"pid":"94501c070c19f283524d47bc1352add6c4a689f3","tid":2461431,"uid":50660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:03:35.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得地產年薪幾多月薪幾多既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de3cb4feeff346c5026ea75e2361c360355a4cd","tid":2461431,"uid":28449,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"e981c805bf9b8cc634b3b61e160b8bc25e191dea","tid":2461431,"uid":66283,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:54:37.000Z","msg":"有冇試過為咗搶單同人打交？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:03:58.000Z","msg":"冇，吾夠大隻，吾會亂來<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc09536567392732544aa81979c7e95cd45a0c24","tid":2461431,"uid":160847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:06:32.000Z","msg":"扑過幾多個mk妹？"},{"pid":"6d4abf14c7786521f07c717669a5a66da8143c42","tid":2461431,"uid":156936,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"作為一個男人，肯衝肯搏，唔怕辛苦，好似30歲未到嘅我，每個月可以攞到千八蚊人工，加上全勤獎金，加上我聰明頭腦，幫老闆開開車門，點點煙，孭下公文包，基本上我可以攞你2千3、4蚊工資，好似我依家咁有錢，我都唔知點樣用，以前我上班，經常都自己帶瓶礦泉水，依家我直接係樓下買，有錢呀嘛，所以話男人呢？一定要唔怕辛苦，唔怕窮，只要你肯努力，遲早有日達到我咁嘅高度，依家我覺得有啲飄，有錢呀嘛，有啲迷失自我。好似前幾日，大嗱嗱花咗幾百蚊染咗呢個髮型，啲錢唔知用喺邊度。依家食煙每支都超過5毫子以上。你哋一定要拼搏，唔好驚辛苦，遲早有日可以達到我嘅高度。"},{"pid":"bc57ea2509d75b4a6462bc1ff76a89cf5efe5ce4","tid":2461431,"uid":28449,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"06d0f82658a64b164f95453cebe77807e4ffdfda","tid":2461431,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:03:15.000Z","msg":"冇可能，少吹水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:08:23.000Z","msg":"8 2定律，大部分的錢俾2成人搵曬，鍾培新都會玩連登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10b58c3f5f041281a64e0628f60828001842028","tid":2461431,"uid":28449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc09536567392732544aa81979c7e95cd45a0c24","tid":2461431,"uid":160847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:06:32.000Z","msg":"扑過幾多個mk妹？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"0<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7331988cb218c91e209e111bbbae8d3c010651","tid":2461431,"uid":103647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ffcf4346e22ec1d9b0a2375ad01b63ee59fd311a","tid":2461431,"uid